## 4. Application Connectivity & Data Integrity
**Objective:** To ensure all features of the PHP application work correctly with the migrated RDS database.

| Test Case ID | Test Category | Procedure | Expected Result | Status |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| **APP-01** | **Query Execution** | Navigate to `index.php` and click on "Data Page" or any category (GDP, Population). | The application should fetch and display data correctly from the `countries` database. | [ ] |
| **APP-02** | **Param Connectivity** | Verify that `get-parameters.php` successfully retrieves settings. | No "SSM Parameter not found" or "Access Denied" errors. | [ ] |
| **APP-03** | **Navigation** | Click through all links: GDP, Population, Life Expectancy, Mortality, Mobile. | All pages should load without 404 or 500 errors. | [ ] |

